The top-right photo shows a man and a woman embracing. The middle-left photo shows a man in a dark sweater, with another person's face redacted by a black box. The middle-right photo is a booking photo of a man. The bottom-left photo is an aerial view of a large complex of buildings. A document identifier is visible at the bottom of the page.
